*************************************
**   Secure Web Api server app     **
*************************************

Example of secure Web API server application

*********** Install notes ***********

Get source code with simple command:
> git clone https://github.com/chval/simple-sec-api.git

Then
> npm install

Create server/.env file with next variables
SEC_API_PORT=8080
SEC_API_SESSION_SECRET=some_secret
SEC_API_SESSION_TTL_MS=60000

Update database
> node server/bin/migrate.js up

Start server
> npm start

Development tools can be found at `server/bin/` directory

